# Markdown Learning
## Level 2 Heading
### Level 3 Heading

## Font
- **overstriking** is using 2 asterisks for both sides
- *italic* is using 1 asterisk for both sides
- ***overstriking + italic*** is using 3 asterisks
- ~~delete~~ is using 2 tildes for both sides

## Quote
> quote is using **a greater than sign + space**

## Partition Line
- one way is using 3 dashes
---

- the other way is using 3 asterisks
***

## Image
- keyboard shortcut is: ![image name](image address)
![example1](data:image/webp;base64,)

## Hyperlink
- [name](address)
- [MyGitHub](https://github.com/NIEr66)

## List
- ordered list
1.

- unorderd list
  - using - with different space
